---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home" language="Markdown" currentFile="README.md">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-white border-b border-[#2b2b2b] pb-2">README.md</h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-6 text-[#cccccc] leading-relaxed">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm bg-[#1e1e1e] p-4 rounded-md border border-[#2b2b2b]">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold text-white shrink-0">
          U
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Your Name</h2>
          <p class="text-blue-400">Software Engineer | Full Stack Developer</p>
          <div class="flex gap-4 mt-2 text-xs">
            <span class="flex items-center gap-1"><span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-400"></span> Available for work</span>
            <span class="text-[#858585]">Based in Location</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>
        Hi, I'm <strong class="text-white">Your Name</strong>. Welcome to my digital workspace. 
        I build high-performance web applications, scalable infrastructure, and CLI tools.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4 border-b border-[#2b2b2b] pb-2">## Core Competencies</h3>
      
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li><strong class="text-blue-400">Frontend:</strong> React, Astro, Next.js, TailwindCSS</li>
        <li><strong class="text-yellow-400">Backend:</strong> Node.js, Python, Go, PostgreSQL</li>
        <li><strong class="text-green-400">Infra/DevOps:</strong> Docker, Kubernetes, AWS, CI/CD</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4 border-b border-[#2b2b2b] pb-2">## Quick Start</h3>
      
      <div class="bg-[#1e1e1e] p-4 rounded-md border border-[#2b2b2b]">
        <code class="text-sm">
          <span class="text-pink-400">const</span> <span class="text-blue-400">explore_portfolio</span> <span class="text-pink-400">=</span> () <span class="text-pink-400">=&gt;</span> {'{'}
          <br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="text-green-400">// Navigate using the Sidebar on the left</span>
          <br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="text-blue-300">openFile</span>(<span class="text-yellow-300">'personal/about.me'</span>);
          <br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="text-blue-300">openFile</span>(<span class="text-yellow-300">'work/experience.ts'</span>);
          <br/>{'}'};
        </code>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>